name: AspGA
tagline: Automatic study plan using Genetic Algorithm.
body:
![AspGA](http://www.genetic-programming.org/ehwlogoellipse.jpg)
## Description

AspGA (Automatic study plan using Genetic Algorithm) is a app that generate a Study Plan for user automatically. It is basically a schedule-weekly that contains the subject and hours necessary to study. This app use [ECJ](http://cs.gmu.edu/~eclab/projects/ecj/)(Evolutionary JAVA-Based computation) framework.
